    "Disposition": {
      "text": "Admission not typically necessary, but should be considered in patients with:\nMyopericarditis\nCardiac tamponade\nHemodynamic instability\nPatients should follow up as an outpatient for repeat inflammatory markers in approximately one month.\n[6]",
